sub_title: Global Recruitment Manager at Stream (NL / US / Global remote)
summary:
Hi there! üëã
I‚Äôm Anastasia, and I‚Äôm currently a Head of Talent Acquisition for the global team of Stream - a Series B startup that powers experiences for over a billion end users with Feeds API & Messaging API. 

If you strive to join us on our way to becoming the AWS of cloud components, either in the Netherlands (Amsterdam) or the USA (Boulder, CO), or remotely across the globe, check out our vacancies over here: https://getstream.io/team/

Note for Stream applicants: I do my best to reply quickly to Linkedin requests, but it does get quite busy here :) Applicants are the greatest priority for our TA team, so please make sure you have applied to the role that you‚Äôre interested in via our website - this way, we will get a chance to respond to your message as quickly as possible and provide you with the best possible candidate experience as well üôå

A bit about myself:

ü¶Ñ Passionate about all things recruitment
üå™ Startups are my element
‚ù§Ô∏è Sharing is caring: co-author and tutor of courses for IT recruiters
üïµÔ∏è‚Äç‚ôÄÔ∏è SOSU speaker (#SOSUHack #SOSUEU) & 2nd place winner of SOSU Sourcing Hackathon 2022
üåà Diversity sourcing toolkit author: https://github.com/gellernastya/diversity-sourcing
üá≥üá± Currently in Amsterdam, Netherlands
üá∫üá¶ Proud Ukrainian

Also, don't be shy to reach out if you're a recruiter seeking consultation - I'm happy to share my experience in exchange for donations to trusted Ukrainian volunteers and NGOs. 

Meeting extraordinary people is the best part of my job for me. 
Feel free to reach out, and let's keep in touchüññ
